(131, 1, '2019-05-30 19:41:24', '2019-05-30 19:41:24', 'Our team has the experience, analytic capabilities and consensus building skills to help your organization with the emotionally charged decision to partner or not? We understand the sensitivities based on our XXXX engagements and the intricacies of the various options you have. We will objectively assess whether and how your organization should pursue partnership opportunities and assist you with the strategic option and partnership selection.', 'Affiliations', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'affiliations', '', '', '2019-05-30 19:41:24', '2019-05-30 19:41:24', '', 0, 'http://localhost/veralon/?post_type=service&#038;p=131', 1, 'service', '', 0),
(132, 1, '2019-05-30 19:41:44', '2019-05-30 19:41:44', 'Veralon has been doing medical staff development planning for decades. We are unusually exacting in our demand methodologies, using market-sensitive indicators rather than applying national figures using Veralon‚Äôs proprietary demand model. Beyond the quantitative analysis, our experts will provide a qualitative analysis that bridges the market dynamics, your organization‚Äôs strategic initiatives and physician need.', 'Medical Staff Planning', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'medical-staff-planning', '', '', '2019-05-30 19:41:44', '2019-05-30 19:41:44', '', 0, 'http://localhost/veralon/?post_type=service&#038;p=132', 2, 'service', '', 0),
